Once again he uses many â€œreligious referencesâ€ ..over a fake gospel sample..and this time goes so far as to slander the names that millions of people deem holy. Calling upon Allah, while referencing himself as JHova in the middle of a Catholic Church?  Itâ€™s just overkill at this point. How many times he gonna film the same slanderous movie?
